title: Looking for High Silver/Low Gold Players for Clash!
body:
Hi guys,

Me and a Friend are looking to make a Clash teams.
He is a Mid main, who peaked Plat 5. I am a ADC Main, who peaked Gold 1. Both of us took a decent break from League and are currently Silver 2.

Looking for a Jungle, Top and Support player for Clash this weekend! If you're interested add jumanjiji! :)
